            "title": "港股開市︱初段偏軟 恒指回吐102點報22589點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股開市初段回吐，恒生指數開市報22589點，跌102點或0.45%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報5185點，跌14點或0.28%；國企指數以8216點開市，跌26點或0.32%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250305_FI_source-web_HSBC-8.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250305_FI_source-web_HSBC-8.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅股普遍回吐，阿里巴巴(09988)開報120.8元，跌0.41%；騰訊(00700)開報487元，跌0.57%；美團(03690)開報139元，暫時無升跌。滙控(00005)開報86.2元，跌1%；友邦(01299)開報61元，跌1.22%</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">衛龍美味(09985)以7.88%折讓價配股，該股今早開報14.82元，跌7.26%；以折讓8.03%配股的老鋪黃金(06181)，今早開報685元，暫時無升跌。近周被蜂巧資本盡沽持股套現22.68億元的泡泡瑪特(09992)，今早開報183.3元，跌0.65%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"衛龍美味官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/09985.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"衛龍美味官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/09985.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">衛龍美味官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">剛公布季績的百威亞太(01876)，今早開報8.43元，跌0.36%；另一業績股宏利金融(00945)則以239.6元開市，暫時無升跌。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今日有兩隻新股登場兩隻，其中滬上阿姨(02589)開報190.6元，較招股價113.12元高68.79%；鈞達(02865)開報22.2元，較招股價22.15元稍微高出0.23%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14911657-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e5%81%8f%e8%bb%9f-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%9b%9e%e5%90%90102%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b122589%e9%bb%9e",
