            "title": "鈞達超購2.5倍近下限定價  耀才暗盤跌2.7%一手蝕60元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">海南鈞達新能源(02865)公布招股價22.15元，近下限定價，香港公開招股超購2.5倍。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"鈞達新能源官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/JTPV.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"鈞達新能源官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/JTPV.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">鈞達新能源官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">鈞達招股價20.4元至28.6元，每手100股。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">一手中籤率23.84%，申請5 手500股穩獲一手。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">輝立暗盤收報22元，跌0.6%，富途暗盤收報21.9元，跌1.1%，耀才暗盤21.55元，跌2.7%，一手蝕60元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14911589-%e9%88%9e%e9%81%94%e8%b6%85%e8%b3%bc2-5%e5%80%8d%e8%bf%91%e4%b8%8b%e9%99%90%e5%ae%9a%e5%83%b9-%e8%80%80%e6%89%8d%e6%9a%97%e7%9b%a4%e8%b7%8c2-7%e4%b8%80%e6%89%8b%e8%9d%9560%e5%85%83",
